<%= section "1. Register to teach a new class in OpenStax Tutor" do %> 

<p>To register to teach a new class in <%= SITE_NAME %>:
  <ol>
        <li><%= link_to "Create an OpenStax Tutor account", new_user_registration_path %>, if you haven't already.</li>
        <p>
        <li>Email <%= email_link "new OST course", "support@openstaxtutor.org" %> and provide the following information:</li>
         <p>
          <ul>
            <li>Name of your institution;</li>
            <li>Full course name (e.g. Math 101: Single-Variable Calculus);</li>
            <li>Short course name (e.g. Math 101);</li>
            <li>Description of the course for the Course Catalog;</li>
            <li>When the class is typically offered, e.g. Fall or Spring. 
          </ul>
          <p>
        <li>Once the administrator confirms your request, go to the <%= link_to "Course Catalog", catalog_path  %> and click <strong>Teach this course</strong>.</li>

               <%= image_tag("teach_this_course.png", {:border => 1, :width => "80%", :height => "80%", :title=>"teach this course"})%>
  <% end %>